# Bourbon framework snippets for Atom Editor

Bourbon snippets to make development faster in Atom.

# Examples

size

```
  @include size(size);
```

marg
```
  @include margin(value);
```

- [See all mixins](#mixins)
- [See all functions](#functions)
- [See all add-ons](#addons)

